Package: country-block
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ipset, iptables, curl
Description: block network traffic by country
 Country Block maintains ipset sets from country IP block lists and applies
 iptables and ip6tables rules for the configured countries, chains, and IP
 versions.
 .
 The package installs a command-line helper, an optional systemd service for
 restoring firewall rules, and an optional scheduled refresh job for keeping
 country lists current.
